HEADWORD: Furbish
<hw>Fur"bish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p.
p.</pos> <conjf>Furbished</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
